---
import AboutHeroImage from "../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg";
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Player profile — who's behind the blog."
	pubDate={new Date("June 06 2026")}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>► PLAYER PROFILE</h2>

	<p>
		Hi, I'm <strong>Bowei</strong> — a developer who likes turning fuzzy ideas
		into things that actually run. This little corner of the internet is where
		I drop notes, half-finished experiments, and whatever I learned the hard way
		this week.
	</p>

	<h3>CLASS: Builder</h3>
	<p>
		I spend most of my time around code — shipping features, breaking things
		in dev, and reading way too many docs. I care about tools that feel
		fast, stay out of the way, and respect the person using them.
	</p>

	<h3>CURRENT QUEST</h3>
	<p>
		I'm building <strong>memex</strong> — a personal memory/knowledge tool inspired
		by Vannevar Bush's 1945 idea of a machine that augments how we think and remember.
		More on that in the blog.
	</p>

	<h3>FAVORITE STAGES</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Small, sharp tools over bloated platforms</li>
		<li>Retro / pixel aesthetics (you may have noticed)</li>
		<li>Writing things down so future-me suffers less</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>► CONTINUE?</h3>
	<p>
		Find me on <a href="https://github.com/Xu929-X1">GitHub</a> or say hi at
		<a href="mailto:boweixu929@gmail.com">boweixu929@gmail.com</a>.
	</p>

	<p><em>Insert coin to keep reading the blog. 🪙</em></p>
</Layout>
